Package: simplejags
Version: 0.01-6
Date: 2014-5-9
Title: Run JAGS from R (a wrapper for rjags)
Author: Ken Kellner <ken@kenkellner.com>
Maintainer: Ken Kellner <ken@kenkellner.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.14.0), rjags (>= 3-3)
Imports: rjags, coda (>= 0.13)
SystemRequirements: jags (>= 3.3.0)
Description: This package runs JAGS (Just Another Gibbs Sampler) analyses from within R. It acts as a wrapper and alternative interface for the functions in the rjags package and adds some custom output and graphical options.
License: GPL (>= 2)
URL: http://code.kenkellner.com/simplejags
NeedsCompilation: no
